{"tid":2292903,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"巴賽雇員:美斯留隊讓我們沮喪 因為要繼續降薪養他","createTime":"2020-11-20T01:00:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-22T04:38:30.000Z","uid":25345,"like":32,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"0307af71554a37dd0d033b6bb35bf17076383919","tid":2292903,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T01:00:23.000Z","msg":"在今年夏天，美斯留在巴賽。對此感到沮喪的，一名巴賽雇員在接受《442》雜志采訪時，坦言部分員工也對此感到很不滿意。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;在美斯決定留隊之後，我們都沮喪。&rdquo;這名雇員說道，&ldquo;大家都是如此，我們知道只是因為俱樂部要支付美斯的薪水，我們大家就要接受更多的降薪。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;我愛美斯，我愛他為巴賽、為足球所做的一切貢獻。&rdquo;這名雇員繼續說道，&ldquo;但我更愛我的家人，更愛我的工作。&rdquo;"},{"pid":"f855a0771cdb56b240e627b18b9aab3d7ad1828e","tid":2292903,"uid":213841,"like":27,"dislike":5,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T01:43:20.000Z","msg":"美斯商業價值咁高 賣波衫都回到本啦 自己垃圾比人炒係到賴地硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d68d8ea3056dd2012c91f9e6bcb7895714784e4","tid":2292903,"uid":10338,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T01:44:56.000Z","msg":"點睇花狗呢隻吸血鬼都仲咁多疤狗撐<br />\n撐到球會破產<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/potion.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/potion.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/potion.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a1b8c5ad03de1716db14cae0cccf65276efb41f","tid":2292903,"uid":25345,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T01:49:40.000Z","msg":"花仔食人血曼頭<br />\n個個減你就50m一年<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45b6625135901e132aa81ca66a1d18e9c555c5d1","tid":2292903,"uid":126044,"like":16,"dislike":10,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T01:49:46.000Z","msg":"唔係美斯fans<br />\n但條友咁講野好on9<br />\n冇人局佢做疤狗<br />\n<br />\n炒撚左美斯份糧俾埋佢好唔好?"},{"pid":"4af83cd9d5a9dc58a0f9aa765ee8df5ab51f20b0","tid":2292903,"uid":142097,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"re